                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 20</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-0000007db29677-3bf4-481b-a624-afc82c2a31e8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017db29677-3bf4-481b-a624-afc82c2a31e8">Make meaningful sentences with the following words:  </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017db29677-3bf4-481b-a624-afc82c2a31e8"><span>            </span></span><span class="pt-0000017db29677-3bf4-481b-a624-afc82c2a31e8"><br />‎</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000027db29677-3bf4-481b-a624-afc82c2a31e8"> </span><span class="pt-0000027db29677-3bf4-481b-a624-afc82c2a31e8">Imminent, Resilient, Thrive, Vigilant, Ephemeral</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007db29677-3bf4-481b-a624-afc82c2a31e8 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000017db29677-3bf4-481b-a624-afc82c2a31e8 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000027db29677-3bf4-481b-a624-afc82c2a31e8 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                        <div class="row solveText" style=" display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4; ">
                                            <p class="pt-00000088010e06-b223-4981-9990-a091d07cf8cd" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000188010e06-b223-4981-9990-a091d07cf8cd">Imminent –</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000288010e06-b223-4981-9990-a091d07cf8cd"> The dark clouds signaled an imminent storm.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000088010e06-b223-4981-9990-a091d07cf8cd {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000188010e06-b223-4981-9990-a091d07cf8cd {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000288010e06-b223-4981-9990-a091d07cf8cd {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000000e52a0f1-fe37-49ce-89a4-bfed6a7e2a44" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000010e52a0f1-fe37-49ce-89a4-bfed6a7e2a44">Resilient –</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000020e52a0f1-fe37-49ce-89a4-bfed6a7e2a44"> Despite many hardships, she remained resilient and hopeful.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000000e52a0f1-fe37-49ce-89a4-bfed6a7e2a44 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000010e52a0f1-fe37-49ce-89a4-bfed6a7e2a44 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000020e52a0f1-fe37-49ce-89a4-bfed6a7e2a44 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000953c3e1e-d493-4ffb-953a-1c96674cafcb" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001953c3e1e-d493-4ffb-953a-1c96674cafcb">Thrive –</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000002953c3e1e-d493-4ffb-953a-1c96674cafcb"> Plants thrive when they receive enough sunlight and water.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000953c3e1e-d493-4ffb-953a-1c96674cafcb {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001953c3e1e-d493-4ffb-953a-1c96674cafcb {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002953c3e1e-d493-4ffb-953a-1c96674cafcb {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000006f1dafa2-4fba-4ec2-8aa8-09213d069f5f" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000016f1dafa2-4fba-4ec2-8aa8-09213d069f5f">Vigilant –</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000026f1dafa2-4fba-4ec2-8aa8-09213d069f5f"> The guard remained vigilant throughout the night.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006f1dafa2-4fba-4ec2-8aa8-09213d069f5f {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000016f1dafa2-4fba-4ec2-8aa8-09213d069f5f {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000026f1dafa2-4fba-4ec2-8aa8-09213d069f5f {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ad5b6fb8-e52f-4552-874a-717ab9f7a631" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001ad5b6fb8-e52f-4552-874a-717ab9f7a631">Ephemeral</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ad5b6fb8-e52f-4552-874a-717ab9f7a631"> – The beauty of a rainbow is </span><span class="pt-000001ad5b6fb8-e52f-4552-874a-717ab9f7a631">ephemeral</span><span class="pt-000001ad5b6fb8-e52f-4552-874a-717ab9f7a631">, lasting only a few moments before it fades.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ad5b6fb8-e52f-4552-874a-717ab9f7a631 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ad5b6fb8-e52f-4552-874a-717ab9f7a631 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000017ce75d-0ecd-4d18-9319-9e71e5e74650" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000017ce75d-0ecd-4d18-9319-9e71e5e74650 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000003bc94faf-9fcb-404a-85e2-c2b8fae19de0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000013bc94faf-9fcb-404a-85e2-c2b8fae19de0">Mark Distribution:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003bc94faf-9fcb-404a-85e2-c2b8fae19de0 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000013bc94faf-9fcb-404a-85e2-c2b8fae19de0 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000189e6a06-54ea-4009-b0a8-6e488c80bfbb" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001189e6a06-54ea-4009-b0a8-6e488c80bfbb">For making meaningful sentence with the following words (0.5&#215;5) =2.5 marks.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000189e6a06-54ea-4009-b0a8-6e488c80bfbb {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001189e6a06-54ea-4009-b0a8-6e488c80bfbb {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007b4dd857-be99-46bf-ba05-042606ee9271" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000017b4dd857-be99-46bf-ba05-042606ee9271">[</span><span class="pt-0000027b4dd857-be99-46bf-ba05-042606ee9271">N.B:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017b4dd857-be99-46bf-ba05-042606ee9271"> Any sentence that is meaningful and correct will get allocated marks]</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007b4dd857-be99-46bf-ba05-042606ee9271 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000017b4dd857-be99-46bf-ba05-042606ee9271 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000027b4dd857-be99-46bf-ba05-042606ee9271 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 21</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-0000003fb54822-d165-48ca-9a6a-33c9c5f3325b" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000013fb54822-d165-48ca-9a6a-33c9c5f3325b">Fill in the blanks with suitable   words from the list below:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000003fb54822-d165-48ca-9a6a-33c9c5f3325b {margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;text-indent: 0.00in;line-height: 108%;}span.pt-0000013fb54822-d165-48ca-9a6a-33c9c5f3325b {font-family: Times New Roman;color: #000000;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000848a1fee-4ab1-4a37-9ffb-19d79c93cc97" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001848a1fee-4ab1-4a37-9ffb-19d79c93cc97">(List: attentive, stress,   creative, harmony, support, respectful)<br />‎  </span><span class="pt-000002848a1fee-4ab1-4a37-9ffb-19d79c93cc97">In order to build a positive and effective   learning environment, both students and teachers must fulfill their roles   with dedication. A good student should always be (a) ______ during lessons,   actively listening and engaging with the content, while also being (b) _____   toward teachers and classmates to maintain a polite and inclusive atmosphere.   On the other hand, teachers should offer emotional and academic (c) ______ to   students who may be experiencing (d) ______ due to pressure or workload. They   must also promote a classroom environment filled with harmony and   understanding, where (e) ______ thinking is encouraged and celebrated as a   part of learning.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000848a1fee-4ab1-4a37-9ffb-19d79c93cc97 {margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;text-indent: 0.00in;line-height: 108%;}span.pt-000001848a1fee-4ab1-4a37-9ffb-19d79c93cc97 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: #000000;font-style: italic;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002848a1fee-4ab1-4a37-9ffb-19d79c93cc97 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: #000000;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                        <div class="row solveText" style=" display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4; ">
                                            <p class="pt-000000c6e98f6b-358f-4538-8809-f19c312e0766" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001c6e98f6b-358f-4538-8809-f19c312e0766">(a) attentive </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000c6e98f6b-358f-4538-8809-f19c312e0766 {margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;text-indent: 0.00in;line-height: 108%;}span.pt-000001c6e98f6b-358f-4538-8809-f19c312e0766 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: #000000;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000999f1ee4-021e-48a1-a4e2-f055bfefab5d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001999f1ee4-021e-48a1-a4e2-f055bfefab5d">(b) respectful </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000999f1ee4-021e-48a1-a4e2-f055bfefab5d {margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;text-indent: 0.00in;line-height: 108%;}span.pt-000001999f1ee4-021e-48a1-a4e2-f055bfefab5d {font-family: Times New Roman;color: #000000;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000028ea6521-2962-4a1d-a161-f5bcf5637658" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-00000128ea6521-2962-4a1d-a161-f5bcf5637658">(c) support</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000028ea6521-2962-4a1d-a161-f5bcf5637658 {margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;text-indent: 0.00in;line-height: 108%;}span.pt-00000128ea6521-2962-4a1d-a161-f5bcf5637658 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: #000000;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000004b928410-aaa6-4bff-a5bf-d98e0e68fa0c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014b928410-aaa6-4bff-a5bf-d98e0e68fa0c">(d) stress </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000004b928410-aaa6-4bff-a5bf-d98e0e68fa0c {margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;text-indent: 0.00in;line-height: 108%;}span.pt-0000014b928410-aaa6-4bff-a5bf-d98e0e68fa0c {font-family: Times New Roman;color: #000000;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000ddd457bf-60b3-4609-b1fe-56cf65aaac75" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001ddd457bf-60b3-4609-b1fe-56cf65aaac75">(e) creative</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ddd457bf-60b3-4609-b1fe-56cf65aaac75 {margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;text-indent: 0.00in;line-height: 108%;}span.pt-000001ddd457bf-60b3-4609-b1fe-56cf65aaac75 {font-family: Times New Roman;color: #000000;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000da44afd7-d0e9-4259-aad2-b7189ce69d6d" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001da44afd7-d0e9-4259-aad2-b7189ce69d6d">Mark Distribution:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000da44afd7-d0e9-4259-aad2-b7189ce69d6d {margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;text-indent: 0.00in;line-height: 108%;}span.pt-000001da44afd7-d0e9-4259-aad2-b7189ce69d6d {font-family: Times New Roman;color: #000000;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000001f7879d0-26eb-47c4-9524-d8bf1d49983e" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000011f7879d0-26eb-47c4-9524-d8bf1d49983e">For filling the blanks with suitable words; (0.5&#215;5) =2.5 marks.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000001f7879d0-26eb-47c4-9524-d8bf1d49983e {margin-top: 0;margin-bottom: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;text-indent: 0.00in;line-height: 108%;}span.pt-0000011f7879d0-26eb-47c4-9524-d8bf1d49983e {font-family: Times New Roman;color: #000000;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 22</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p class="pt-000000ce8bb883-6711-4a9e-b70a-3f9fb882e790" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ce8bb883-6711-4a9e-b70a-3f9fb882e790">Write a well organised paragraph on </span><span class="pt-000002ce8bb883-6711-4a9e-b70a-3f9fb882e790">‘The Value of Time’</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001ce8bb883-6711-4a9e-b70a-3f9fb882e790"> in the space provided, considering the element of a paragraph, such as topic sentence, supporting detail sentences and conclusion.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000ce8bb883-6711-4a9e-b70a-3f9fb882e790 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001ce8bb883-6711-4a9e-b70a-3f9fb882e790 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002ce8bb883-6711-4a9e-b70a-3f9fb882e790 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                        <div class="row solveText" style=" display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4; ">
                                            <p class="pt-000000b6a58942-b9a8-4a21-aad9-ed97753263cb" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001b6a58942-b9a8-4a21-aad9-ed97753263cb">‘The Value of Time’</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000b6a58942-b9a8-4a21-aad9-ed97753263cb {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001b6a58942-b9a8-4a21-aad9-ed97753263cb {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000042edd6f4-211b-4563-b5db-0ab0599dfade" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000142edd6f4-211b-4563-b5db-0ab0599dfade">Time is one of the most precious resources in our lives, and once lost, it can never be regained. It waits for no one and moves forward constantly, making it essential to use every moment wisely. People who understand the value of time tend to lead more disciplined, productive, and successful lives. Time management helps us set priorities, meet deadlines, and reduce stress. Wasting time, on the other hand, leads to missed opportunities </span><span class="pt-00000142edd6f4-211b-4563-b5db-0ab0599dfade">and regret. Whether in studies, work, or personal growth, using time effectively brings long-term benefits. Therefore, we must respect time and make the best use of it to build a brighter future.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000042edd6f4-211b-4563-b5db-0ab0599dfade {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000142edd6f4-211b-4563-b5db-0ab0599dfade {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a70012bd-1a11-4c28-aecd-a817435e37bc" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-000001a70012bd-1a11-4c28-aecd-a817435e37bc">Marks Distribution:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a70012bd-1a11-4c28-aecd-a817435e37bc {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a70012bd-1a11-4c28-aecd-a817435e37bc {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000a20911e5-47c4-4a8e-9fbe-f40951dcc079" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001a20911e5-47c4-4a8e-9fbe-f40951dcc079">For writing Title, </span><span class="pt-000002a20911e5-47c4-4a8e-9fbe-f40951dcc079">‘The Value of Time’; 0.5 mark.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000a20911e5-47c4-4a8e-9fbe-f40951dcc079 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001a20911e5-47c4-4a8e-9fbe-f40951dcc079 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002a20911e5-47c4-4a8e-9fbe-f40951dcc079 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-000000473e5bcd-5041-4875-a07b-141bdf3497fd" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001473e5bcd-5041-4875-a07b-141bdf3497fd">For writing topic sentence such as, </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001473e5bcd-5041-4875-a07b-141bdf3497fd">People who understand the value of time tend to lead more disciplined, productive, and successful lives. Time management helps us set priorities, meet deadlines, and reduce stress. </span><span class="pt-000002473e5bcd-5041-4875-a07b-141bdf3497fd">1.5 marks.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000473e5bcd-5041-4875-a07b-141bdf3497fd {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001473e5bcd-5041-4875-a07b-141bdf3497fd {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-000002473e5bcd-5041-4875-a07b-141bdf3497fd {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000009b8a28dd-768b-48de-9673-a48f756e8f08" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000019b8a28dd-768b-48de-9673-a48f756e8f08">For writing supporting detail sentences such as, </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000019b8a28dd-768b-48de-9673-a48f756e8f08">Time management helps us set priorities, meet deadlines, and reduce stress. Wasting time, on the other hand, leads to missed opportunities and regret. Whether in studies, work, or personal growth, using time effectively brings long-term benefits. </span><span class="pt-0000029b8a28dd-768b-48de-9673-a48f756e8f08">1.5 marks.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000009b8a28dd-768b-48de-9673-a48f756e8f08 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000019b8a28dd-768b-48de-9673-a48f756e8f08 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000029b8a28dd-768b-48de-9673-a48f756e8f08 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000004745fdf6-32d6-4725-8bb5-1f87bacf3a46" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014745fdf6-32d6-4725-8bb5-1f87bacf3a46">For writing conclusion such as, </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000014745fdf6-32d6-4725-8bb5-1f87bacf3a46">whether in studies, work, or personal growth, using time effectively brings long-term benefits. Therefore, we must respect time and make the best use of it to build a brighter future; </span><span class="pt-0000024745fdf6-32d6-4725-8bb5-1f87bacf3a46">1.5 marks.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000004745fdf6-32d6-4725-8bb5-1f87bacf3a46 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000014745fdf6-32d6-4725-8bb5-1f87bacf3a46 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000024745fdf6-32d6-4725-8bb5-1f87bacf3a46 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000006cdf4305-781d-4d30-a009-b05441cb9ec4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000016cdf4305-781d-4d30-a009-b05441cb9ec4">[</span><span class="pt-0000026cdf4305-781d-4d30-a009-b05441cb9ec4">Instructions:</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006cdf4305-781d-4d30-a009-b05441cb9ec4 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000016cdf4305-781d-4d30-a009-b05441cb9ec4 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000026cdf4305-781d-4d30-a009-b05441cb9ec4 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000002e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c">* Students must write it within one single para. If it becomes </span><span class="pt-0000022e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c">more than one para</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c">, </span><span class="pt-0000022e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c">50% marks</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c"> have to be </span><span class="pt-0000022e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c">deducted</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000012e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c"> from the </span><span class="pt-0000022e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c">obtained marks.</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000002e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000012e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-0000022e1534c9-a33a-4858-89dd-506cd19be70c {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-00000009e79102-37f9-493d-87a4-b022b9cd9eaa" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000109e79102-37f9-493d-87a4-b022b9cd9eaa">* 0.5 mark will be </span><span class="pt-00000209e79102-37f9-493d-87a4-b022b9cd9eaa">deducted for one or two grammar or spelling mistakes</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-00000109e79102-37f9-493d-87a4-b022b9cd9eaa">, 01 mark </span><span class="pt-00000209e79102-37f9-493d-87a4-b022b9cd9eaa">for three or more grammar or spelling mistakes</span><span class="pt-00000109e79102-37f9-493d-87a4-b022b9cd9eaa">.]</span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-00000009e79102-37f9-493d-87a4-b022b9cd9eaa {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-00000109e79102-37f9-493d-87a4-b022b9cd9eaa {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}span.pt-00000209e79102-37f9-493d-87a4-b022b9cd9eaa {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p>
